    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classQFieldCloudStatus" kindref="compound">QFieldCloudStatus</ref> fetches the QFieldCloud service status endpoint and exposes the health state of the service to QML.</para>
<para>It fetches the /api/v1/status/ endpoint once per session and provides properties to determine whether the service is degraded, has ongoing incidents, or is under maintenance. </para>
